stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> AwaitingQuestion
    AwaitingQuestion --> Generating: question_received
    Generating --> AwaitingFeedback: answer_streamed
    AwaitingFeedback --> AwaitingQuestion: feedback_yes / reset counter
    AwaitingFeedback --> AwaitingQuestion: feedback_no [counter < 3] / increment counter
    AwaitingFeedback --> Escalated: feedback_no [counter >= 3]
    Escalated --> [*]: escalate_to_human

    note right of AwaitingFeedback
      Show "Did this answer your question?"
      Yes resets counter
      No increments counter
    end note

    note right of Escalated
      Offer escalate_to_human
      End current session
    end note